Using NodeMUD (Ranvier MUD) as a skeleton, Fickle is analyzing the code
to learn more about Node, and the Node server programming architecture.  Since
this is a project in progress, expect change.  Expect change often.  Expect 
downtime, crashes and even occasional cursing and gnashing of teeth.